            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: National Clinical Guideline Centre. Anaemia management in people with chronic kidney disease. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2011 Feb. 38 p. (Clinical guideline; no. 114).</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
