 (271737000), <a href="/web/20180712184224/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0002873&amp;fLockTerm=Anemia+of+chronic+disease">Anemia of chronic disease</a>
 (234347009), <a href="/web/20180712184224/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0005774&amp;fLockTerm=Blood+chemistry">Blood chemistry</a>
